{"tid":2517074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"表彰民主抗爭 港人上屆得主","createTime":"2021-05-05T05:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T08:22:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d55a143b590f5b001a03b76280b95dd7ad0451","tid":2517074,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210505/E24OCOBQXRHXDBON3BLHTVQGGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210505%2FE24OCOBQXRHXDBON3BLHTVQGGQ%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=2aa7c8b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210505%2FE24OCOBQXRHXDBON3BLHTVQGGQ%2F&h=671219bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210505/E24OCOBQXRHXDBON3BLHTVQGGQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n表彰民主抗爭 港人上屆得主<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NcOput_8j2asjoNIFoDAcx12gaA=/510x596/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4RPN7YNYM5HY7BVDSHRIRBTDXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNcOput_8j2asjoNIFoDAcx12gaA%3D%2F510x596%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4RPN7YNYM5HY7BVDSHRIRBTDXU.jpg&h=b68f5c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2019年的麥凱恩獎得主是參與反修例示威的「香港人」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】總部設在美國、獲加拿大贊助的非政府組織哈利法克斯論壇，於三年前起設麥凱恩公共服務領袖獎（下稱麥凱恩獎）。獎項是以已故美國聯邦參議員麥凱恩為名，以紀念其堅定追求自由、平等、機會與民主價值。授予此獎項的對象必須經由麥凱恩參議員的遺孀同意，台灣總統蔡英文則為麥凱恩獎的第三屆得主。<br />\n<br />\n至於前屆得主為「反送中」運動的「香港人」，獎項以嘉勉港人為保有權利、推動民主改革抗爭。當時由時任民陣副召集人陳皓桓、民主黨前主席劉慧卿前往加拿大作為代表領獎。首屆得主則為希臘列士波斯島人民，以表彰他們拯救難民的義舉。據資料顯示，論壇每年均在加拿大哈利法克斯舉辦，並廣邀各國政府官員、軍方代表、學術界和商界共同參與。論壇去年更曾發表報告，批評「中共才是危害世界的病毒」，並指世界因為疫情對中國的威脅覺醒。"},{"pid":"320cc65458ec888af88ea0e26932a19b23666d89","tid":2517074,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5a63c978731ae531b233457ecfa4d7429d85a5","tid":2517074,"uid":342828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"0169dfb2ccdf69bac3c4ea84ee7cba89b5641e11","tid":2517074,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ae169b3c9f384189364b7a03aa0a0416b34d2a","tid":2517074,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-jxexRZFuJA/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F-jxexRZFuJA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=448e4626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/tw-tsai-05042021050052.html/tw-tsai2.jpg/@@images/b423de81-0ca9-46c8-98dc-57a5fefb105e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Ftw-tsai-05042021050052.html%2Ftw-tsai2.jpg%2F%40%40images%2Fb423de81-0ca9-46c8-98dc-57a5fefb105e.jpeg&h=db3af845&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}